text: Christa Winkel (born 28 April 1959) is an Austrian equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Austria Category:Equestrians at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
